flowchart TD
    A[Online Runs] --> T[Governance + Trace]
    T --> E[Offline Evaluation]
    E --> F[Metrics + Failure Taxonomy + Safety Findings]
    F --> R{Regression or Risk Found?}
    R -->|yes| O[Update Orchestration Policy]
    R -->|yes| C[Update Tools / Retrieval / Model Routing]
    O --> G[Versioned Evaluation + Release Gate]
    C --> G
    G -->|pass| D[Deploy]
    G -->|fail| X[Revise Candidate Changes]
    X --> O
    X --> C
    D --> A
    R -->|no| B[Keep Baseline + Continue Monitoring]
    B --> A
